<br>
Waking the sleeper to set guilds back would only set T2 guilds back for a short period of time. There are still many places to equip that are equal to or better than ST. The main reason everyone wants ST to stay asleep I think is because of those couple cool items (I say cool because the Gnome Mask isn't exactly vital) and because it's easy to get good weapons and also because getting to ST is a rite of passage just like getting to the planes for the first time, VP, Vex Thal, HS, Seb etc.<br>
<br>
I think Reso has earned the right to wake the sleeper since they were there first, but I don't think they should. On the other hand, if they leave him up and some T2 guild gets in there, pharms the place then wakes him just to get the &quot;server first&quot; out from under Reso, it will create a shitstorm the likes of which this server has never seen.<br>
